    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 it is sold strictly as-is and is best suited for buyers comfortable taking on a project car or those simply needing basic, budget transportation. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust, dents, and paint damage that go beyond cosmetic concerns. The interior is worn and tired, with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable daily-driver status \u2014 buyers should budget for additional work beyond the purchase price. There are no recent service records to speak of, and we make no representations about the drivetrain's long-term reliability. That said, the vehicle does run and move under its own power. This is an honest, transparent listing: if you're a hands-on buyer, a mechanic, or someone looking for a parts car or fixer-upper at a fair entry price, this may be the right opportunity for you.",
